# javax.* to jakarta.* Namespace Migration Skill

## Overview
Spring Boot 3.x / Spring Framework 6.x requires Jakarta EE 9+ APIs. All "'`javax.*` imports from Java EE must be replaced with `jakarta.*`.

## Affected Packages

| Old (javax)                  | New (jakarta)                  |
